text: Blabia cristulata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Martins and Galileo in 1995. It is known from Colombia and Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Blabia cristulata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Blabia Category:Beetles described in 1995
title: Blabia cristulata
